02:47.680 --> 02:50.149
That's why I had you assigned here, Bram.

02:50.150 --> 02:53.659
So you could witness Giller's twist alchemy for yourself

02:53.660 --> 02:57.010
I'd hoped your accounts of what went on here
were exaggerated, Uncle.

02:57.700 --> 02:58.769
But that woman--

02:58.770 --> 03:00.819
That woman was one of the lucky ones.

03:00.820 --> 03:02.370
At least she died.

03:02.680 --> 03:05.169
d the more Rahl pushes Giller for results,

03:05.170 --> 03:08.040
the more sadistic his experiments become.

03:13.090 --> 03:18.560
For too long, I've sat idly by while Rahl has waged his war in the name of peace.

03:18.680 --> 03:20.562
And now I'm supposed to watch as he has his Wizard

03:20.562 --> 03:23.122
butcher defenseless women and children?

03:24.500 --> 03:26.960
Lord Rahl must have his reasons.

03:27.520 --> 03:29.329
If Giller succeeds,

03:29.330 --> 03:33.320
Rahl will no longer need the Boxes of Orden
to control us all.

03:33.480 --> 03:36.560
We'll all be enslaved to his will.

03:37.170 --> 03:38.930
Captain Ericon.

03:43.220 --> 03:47.449
Inform Lord Rahl that we are making progress

03:47.450 --> 03:50.970
despite today's, uh, disappointment.

03:51.400 --> 03:53.260
Yes, Wizard.

03:54.731 --> 03:58.930
We're running out of places to bury Giller's disappointmes.

04:00.610 --> 04:01.870
You're right.

04:02.160 --> 04:03.690
This is madness.

04:03.950 --> 04:06.653
But defying Rahl is just as insane.

04:06.653 --> 04:10.700
If we don't act soon,
defying Rahl will no longer be an option.

04:17.209 --> 04:20.329
Lord Rahl, word from Edraan.

04:31.340 --> 04:34.539
It appears Wizard Giller mighhave more success

04:34.540 --> 04:36.790
if he had the proper motivation.

04:37.390 --> 04:38.920
Send a reply.

04:40.230 --> 04:42.720
My dear Giller...

04:46.920 --> 04:48.149
What is it?

04:48.150 --> 04:51.159
When the Constellation of Pirion aligns,

04:51.160 --> 04:53.810
Lord Rahl will arrive at the Keep.

04:53.910 --> 04:58.640
He's coming to oversee Giller's work personally.

05:02.060 --> 05:03.760
And when he gets here,

05:04.900 --> 05:06.850
we're going to kill him.

